subject: WP Engine wins Gold Stevie Award for customer service excellence
body:
A gold standard in customer support 
WP Engine’s Customer Experience team earns top honors at this year’s Stevie Awards.
 
Find Out More Here 
 
A HISTORY OF EXCELLENCE IN SERVICE
Recognized leadership in customer support 
At WP Engine, customer satisfaction is more than a goal—it’s a driving force. That’s why we’re proud to announce that our Customer Experience (CX) team has earned the prestigious 
Gold Stevie Award
 for Customer Service Department of the Year in the Computer Services category! 
 
This incredible honor marks another major achievement in our long-standing history of excellence in customer service. Since 2015, WP Engine has won more than a dozen Stevie Awards, and our CX team is at the heart of this success. Continually setting the bar for exceptional support, their tireless dedication ensures that every customer experience is 
Customer-Inspired
. 
 
Here’s why this recognition is so special: 
Marks our 11th Stevie Award for customer support and our 15th Stevie Award overall
Highlights over a decade of consistent achievement at The Stevie Awards
Underscores the dedication and commitment of our incredible support agents  
Thank you to our amazing CX team and customers for making this possible. Let’s keep raising the bar together! 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
WP Engine, 504 Lavaca St, #1000, Austin,TX 78701

subject: Join Dr. Kellee Franklin for a Bold Conversation on AI & Work
body:
AI Meets Empathy: A Webinar You Don’t Want to Miss 
 
 
Everyone’s talking about AI. 
But how many are talking about the people behind it?
On 
Tuesday, April 8
, we’re bringing you a very different kind of conversation, one that puts 
humans
 at the center of the AI revolution. 
We’re joined by 
Dr. Kellee Franklin,
 innovation strategist, educator, and someone who’s spent years helping leaders rethink what transformation really looks like. 
Together, we’ll dig into questions like:
What does a truly human-centric workplace look like in the age of AI? 
How do we empower people to grow 
with
 technology, not around it? 
And what are the global companies getting right about the Human+AI advantage?
      
Date:

Thank you for being part of the 
2025 Global Innovation Summit
. Your presence and engagement helped shape meaningful conversations that are still resonating today.

Global Innovation Communities

Sign up

These communities connect professionals and thought leaders across sectors to explore today’s most pressing innovation themes, including:
Digital Transformation & Emerging Technologies
 
Sustainability & Climate Innovation
 
Smart Cities & Urban Development

Education & Lifelong Learning
 
Finance & FinTech Innovation
 
Innovation in Government Services
